org.apache.paimon.deletionvectors

Interface DeletionVector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BitmapDeletionVector

    public interface DeletionVector
    The DeletionVector can efficiently record the positions of rows that are deleted in a file, which can then be used to filter out deleted rows when processing the file.
